>.<

Title: Sort Workers in Ascending Order by First Name and Descending Order by Department
Link: https://platform.stratascratch.com/coding/9836-sort-workers-in-ascending-order-by-the-first-name-and-in-descending-order-by-department-name?code_type=3
Level: Easy

Sort workers in ascending order by the first name and then in descending order by department name.

Data worker:
worker_id: bigint
first_name: text
last_name: text
salary: bigint
joining_date: datetime
department: text

>.<

Solution:

select concat(first_name,' ',last_name) fullname
from worker
order by first_name asc, department desc;
    
Output:

fullname
Agepi Argon
Amitah Singh
Geetika Chauhan
Jai Patel
Moe Acharya
Monika Arora
Nayah Laghari
Niharika Verma
Satish Kumar
Vipul Diwan
Vishal Singhal
Vivek Bhati
